  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the clay tajine to 425\u00192F (220\u001aC).",
    "Mix flax eggs, cumin, coriander, turmeric, and salt in a bowl.",
    "Add chopped onion, carrot, and potato to the bowl and mix well.",
    "Add broken cauliflower and minced red chili pepper to the bowl and mix well.",
    "Brush the clay tajine with a little oil and layer the vegetable mixture.",
    "Pour ginger paste, flax eggs mixture, and lime juice over the vegetables.",
    "Cover the clay tajine and roast in the preheated oven for 30 minutes.",
    "Remove cover and continue roasting for another 15 minutes or until the potatoes are tender and the cauliflower is golden brown.",
    "Remove the clay tajine from the oven and let it cool for a few minutes.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with fresh cilantro or scallions."
  ],
